# Example Agent Folder Structure

```
Agents/JsonAgent/
├── Agent/                     # Core agent functionality
│   ├── agentTools.py          # Tools for the agent to interact with JSON
│   ├── graph.py               # Graph of state machine defining agent's behavior
│   ├── prompt.py              # Prompt templates for the agent and agent instantiation
│   ├── agentState.py          # Agent state management
│   ├── __init__.py            # Package initialization
│   └── testFiles/             # Test files for agent components
│
├── operations/                # Implementations of operations agent can perform
│   ├── crudOperations.py     # Example of operations
│   ├── __init__.py            # Package initialization
│   └── README.md              # Operations documentation
│
├── launcher/                  # Agent launcher and interface
│   ├── chat.py                # Chat interface
│   ├── commandHandler.py      # Command handling logic
│   ├── commandLine.py         # Command line interface
│   ├── __main__.py            # Entry point
│   ├── __init__.py            # Package initialization
│   └── *.json                 # Sample/test JSON files
│
├── tests/                     # Test suite
│   ├── test_*.py              # Various test modules for different functionalities
│   ├── SCENARIOS.md           # Test scenarios documentation
│   └── __init__.py            # Package initialization
│
├── logs/                      # Log files directory (empty)
│
├── resources/                 # Images and other resources
│
├── __init__.py                # Package initialization
├── TODO.md                    # Todo list
├── ALREADY_DONE.md            # Completed tasks
├── SETUP.md                   # Setup instructions
├── TERMS.md                   # Terminology definitions
└── .cursorignore              # Cursor IDE ignore file
``` 